        {% include 'icon-bubble-exclamation' %}
        {% include 'icon-yield-sign' %}
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-4">
        <p class="HeaderA-Level4">What Is A Security Alert?</p>
        <p>A security alert is a notification of a particular event that has occurred. It’s sent to those responsible for investigating further. The SIEM handles the alerts to keep everyone in the loop.</p>
        <p class="HeaderA-Level4">What Is A Security Incident?</p>
        <p>A security incident is an event that resulted in damage that negatively effected the confidentiality, integrity or availability of a business. An incident needs attention immediately to properly resolve or mitgate the impact.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
